optional_filter_rules: CASE WHEN src_env_sk in ('480', '490') THEN (NOT (anaacd IS NULL)) AND (NOT (CAST(string_like(CAST(upper(anaacd) AS STRING), '%TEST%') AS BOOLEAN) OR CAST(string_like(CAST(upper(anaacd) AS STRING), '%TST%') AS BOOLEAN))) ELSE (NOT (anaacd IS NULL)) AND (((CAST(rccesp_lkp_match0 AS BOOLEAN) AND (coalesce(niiyc31, ' ') = 'Y')) OR ((NOT CAST(rccesp_lkp_match0 AS BOOLEAN)) AND (CAST(rccesp_lkp_match2 AS BOOLEAN) AND (coalesce(niiyc33, ' ') = 'Y')))) OR ((niiyc31 IS NULL) AND (coalesce(niiyc33, ' ') = 'Y'))) END
reformat_rules:
{
  "carrier_acct_sk": "-1",
  "acct_client_type_desc": "acct_client_type_desc2",
  "acct_client_type_id": "acct_client_type_id2",
  "acct_product_line_id": "acct_product_line_id2",
  "acct_product_type_desc": "acct_product_type_desc2",
  "acct_product_type_id": "acct_product_type_id2",
  "hm_dlvry_stat_ind": "'N'",
  "hm_dlvry_only_ind": "'N'",
  "carrier_sk": "in1_carrier_sk",
  "account_nm": "CASE WHEN (isNullOrBlank(acct_nm1) OR (acct_nm1 = '-')) THEN anbjtx ELSE acct_nm1 END",
  "acct_product_line_desc": "acct_product_line_desc2",
  "account_id": "anaccd",
  "carrier_id": "anaacd",
  "carrier_nm": "CASE WHEN isNullOrBlank(carrier_nm0) THEN carrier_nm1 ELSE carrier_nm0 END",
  "rebates_stat_ind": "'N'",
  "rebates_only_ind": "'N'",
  "src_env_sk": "CAST(src_env_sk AS DECIMAL(38,0))",
  "rec_sts": "'Y'"
}
